{"tid":2035949,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"20年前賭王為慈善與肥姐趙薇合唱　一曲與四太訂情","createTime":"2020-05-26T07:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:15:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8347fd58a7b01a3570697de14154eca377b76519","tid":2035949,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:41:37.000Z","msg":"賭王何鴻燊今日（26/5）逝世，終年98歲，畢生為事業打拼，與看似與音樂沒太大關係，不過一代賭王其實也曾經因慈善而公開演唱。2000年，由蕭芳芳一力促成的籌款節目《護苗基金星輝夜》在TVB上直播，當時邀得何鴻燊分別與肥姐合唱Nat King Cole的經典作品《Pretend》，以及與趙薇合唱鄧麗君的《月亮代表我的心》。<br />\n<br />\n提起《月亮代表我的心》，其實還有一個關於賭王的故事。何鴻燊與四太梁安琪的三子何猷君，曾表示自己在媽媽生日上為她自彈自唱《月亮代表我的心》作為生日禮物。根據何猷君講述，之所以選擇這首歌，是因為他知道爸爸何鴻燊和媽媽梁安琪當年談戀愛時就是唱這首鄧麗君經典。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_qlDM8_7Qho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_qlDM8_7Qho&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY5LdSN32AczdJcE5lfwVwJ8%3D&h=e38eecfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_qlDM8_7Qho</a>"},{"pid":"ac23df816890a8ac0ffa214e56cff35eaaa499ee","tid":2035949,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"賭王唱歌好難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d129d50b63a0b79150623db9485ab19ba585eb0","tid":2035949,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac23df816890a8ac0ffa214e56cff35eaaa499ee","tid":2035949,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"賭王唱歌好難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉"}]}